      <title>合氣道の思想と技【第0347回】　以心導引</title>
      <link>https://kaku-budo.github.io/blog/aikido/philosophy/part-0301-0400/p-0347-heart-lead-love/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 11 Jan 2026 19:29:00 +0800</pubDate>
      <guid>https://kaku-budo.github.io/blog/aikido/philosophy/part-0301-0400/p-0347-heart-lead-love/</guid>
      <description>&lt;style&gt;
  /* 1. 標題縮小 */
  .post-title, h1 { font-size: 28px !important; color: #2c3e50 !important; }

  /* 2. 粗體變道服藍 (與暗色模式相容) */
